title: PLA Unit 61486
added: Their exposure came after another [[PLA Unit 61398]] was exposed for similar activity the previous year, as well as the indictment of five members of Unit 61398 by the United States the previous month.<ref name="nyt">{{cite news|last1=Perlroth|first1=Nicole|title=2nd China Army Unit Implicated in Online Spying|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/10/technology/private-report-further-details-chinese-cyberattacks.html|accessdate=9 June 2014|work=The New York Times|date=9 June 2014}} Meanwhile, Snowden’s release of information on America’s surveillance program would also become a focus of China’s response to the accusations of spying, claiming the United States was hypocritical in their accusations of espionage.<ref name="Private U.S. report accuses another Chinese military unit of hacking">{{cite news |last1=Menn |first1=Joseph |title=Private U.S. report accuses another Chinese military unit of hacking |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-cybersecurity-china/private-u-s-report-accuses-another-chinese-military-unit-of-hacking-idUSKBN0EL0N420140610 |accessdate=15 October 2020 |agency=Reuters |date=10/6/2014}}</ref>
